      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>A series of letters from Rotha to his wife, containing personal and professional observations during his early career in England and in New York. Also, one letter from Rotha to Peter Hunt.</p>
         <p/>
      </scopecontent>
